{"tid":177390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲司機，開車時偶遇袋鼠，結果差點被袋鼠暴打！","createTime":"2017-03-28T22:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T05:14:30.000Z","uid":3203,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf4d0a1e5a19b50cefa6cf00910a46e159c54fbf","tid":177390,"uid":3203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T22:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn-news.china.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/640-6-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-news.china.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F640-6-1.jpeg&h=b6afb5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《每日郵報》報道，在澳洲首都堪培拉，就有這麼一位司機，偶遇一隻得了路怒症的袋鼠，結果差點就被一頓暴錘！<br />\n事情是這樣的&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n本來呢，人家司機當天是要趕夜路去一個地方。<br />\n正在路上開的好好的呢，突然，燈光下就出現了一隻袋鼠！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-news.china.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/0-1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-news.china.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F0-1.gif&h=53694c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司機趕緊減慢速度停下車，可是，還是被我們的澳洲第一壯漢發現了！<br />\n「我在路上跳的好好的，為什麼要拿這麼亮的燈來照我？！」<br />\n袋鼠大爺很生氣，你的後果很嚴重！<br />\n發現了身後的燈光，袋鼠也不走了，轉過頭就盯住了汽車！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-news.china.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/0-2-1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-news.china.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F0-2-1.gif&h=7a978ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-news.china.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/0-3-1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-news.china.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F0-3-1.gif&h=9555e7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位土澳第一壯，頗有黑社會大哥的架勢，嘴裏還叼着個煙！（其實是根草啦）<br />\n衝上前來，對着車就是一通毒打，這場面可把司機嚇得不輕，趕緊鎖好門窗，連大氣也不敢出&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n這要是下了車，被暴打的可就是自己了啊！<br />\n對着車子打了半天，估計是也有點累了，這位第一壯，終於是停了手，又盯着車看了半天，才意猶未盡的跳開了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-news.china.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/s640.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-news.china.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fs640.jpeg&h=966cb588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-news.china.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/640-4-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-news.china.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F640-4-1.jpeg&h=eec30c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-news.china.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/640-5-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-news.china.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F640-5-1.jpeg&h=2f4dd3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你仲叼住條草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2f353f4b8a3ed75ae6f2be324646870d1e5196","tid":177390,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:04:26.000Z","msg":"叼住口煙(草) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257a948957576adeee17ca77d3f12b5be5e685bd","tid":177390,"uid":7704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e310bb89c50e76779b18eafc152446b581cdcbf5","tid":177390,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300d90abf5630ff1728598f9f716f932e16ed120","tid":177390,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:20:46.000Z","msg":"澳洲動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdc3b8f892880a7ed234623380534424502d45f","tid":177390,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-